{
  "texts": [
    "The ArabicText 2022 corpus is the world's largest opensource pretraining dataset for Arabic, specifically designed for training Arabic LLMs.",
    "The creators curate, expand, and clean existing Arabic web text data, resulting in a dataset of 201.9GB.",
    "Text and knowledge-related data constitute over 65% of the corpus.",
    "• Dolma (Soldaini et al, 2024).",
    "The Dolma corpus is a vast English-language corpus comprising 3T tokens."
  ]
}